description: This common Cooter purrs with a rating of 14, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 14, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, Stringalong for East, 8 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [14 Votes, Common]
